headline: Waste Connections Stock Slides 7% Since Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates
summary: WCN shares fall 7% since fourth-quarter 2025 earnings topped estimates, as margin pressure, an operating loss and weaker recycling results weigh on sentiment.
